      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been meticulously cared for, kept in a garage, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. If you're looking for something that's basically perfect, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
