    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated precision. The S54 inline-six features a documented high-pressure VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment within the last 500 miles. Power delivery is linear and aggressive, channeled through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential. The chassis is structurally pristine, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with a specialized epoxy-injection and plate kit. Suspension kinematics are tight, utilizing fresh OEM bushings and Sachs dampers to maintain factory-intended roll centers. The exterior retains its original depth and clarity with zero evidence of thermal cycling on the trim or oxidation on the undercarriage. This is an investment-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
