    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from any swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the alloy wheels are entirely devoid of curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car scent; the high-grade leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, bolstering, or creasing. All electronic systems, from the premium surround-sound audio to the intuitive navigation interface, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule\u2014full documentation of which is available for review. This is not merely a used car; it is a turn-key collector-quality machine that drives as sharply as the day it left the assembly line.",
