    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This example is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by M-tuned suspension and a functional limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and flawless paint depth measurements confirm its climate-controlled history. A turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
